<p class="title">Use Case Message</p>
<br>
<p>George wants to message Robert and ask him some questions about a cartridge he recently put up on the site.  He logs into Cartridge Coders and he fills out the messaging form and sends it to Robert.  Robert checks his email and notices that a user of Cartridge Coders has a few questions about an item he has for sale.  He logs in and answers the questions.</p>
